										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>This is the first blockmesh level that I have ever created. It was a one month assignment for my class. Below I will show you the reference images I used as well as the final result of the blockmesh. I haven&#8217;t had much experience designing things like this in the past, but creating this level changed my perspective and gave me more motivation to work on similar projects in the future.</p>



