<p class="has-large-font-size">This is the start of my level. The player looks at a mountain with a cave entrance. There are two statues holding a sword, with the red square symbolizing a shield of some sort. (I realize I could have used a circle, but didn&#8217;t think of it at the time)</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill" style="grid-template-columns:38% auto;"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media" style="background-image:url('/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint.png?w=1024');background-position:50% 50%;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1916" height="1032" src="/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-76 size-large" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint.png 1916w, /wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint-300x162.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint-1024x552.png 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint-768x414.png 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2021/08/m_jurado_mb1_focalpoint-1536x827.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1916px) 100vw, 1916px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
